      143.95
    ],
    "text": "Two Suspects Arrested in Connection with Fatal Sharp-Weapon Attack \u2013 Sahaspura Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      158.41,
      523.85,
      199.29
    ],
    "text": "Sahaspura Police initiated investigations into the murder of an individual who was fatally attacked with a sharp weapon in the Halgahawatta area of the Sahaspura Police Division during the early hours of 03.06.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      213.73,
      514.23,
      254.64
    ],
    "text": "Following extensive inquiries, a team of officers from the Sahaspura Police Station arrested two suspects in the Madampitiya area on 05.06.2026 in connection with the homicide.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      269.2,
      412.39,
      282.48
    ],
    "text": "The suspects, aged 21 and 23, are residents of the Borella area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      297.04,
      436.06,
      310.32
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Sahaspura Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
